"So I should end up with 12 units regardless of whether the swap happens right? Doesn't this mean that I can waitlist in a different 4 unit class during the ongoing phase 2?"

No, because you've enrolled in 12 units and also reserved your spot in another 4 unit class, so the system sees that you're in 16 units. It's arguably a glitch that you can enroll in 12 units and then waitlist in another 4, but either way you won't be able to add another 4 unit class in phase 2, as you've seen
